{
  "stem": "15962.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I did lose one school year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't go immediately to the grade I belonged for my age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I did go to school there for three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In 1946, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my uncle, who spent the war in Palestine with his family, returned to Nachod and insisted that I stay with him.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He just felt that he respected, whether I liked it or not, it was his duty to his sister, deceased sister, that he takes care of me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So very reluctantly, I moved to their house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had a son two years younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We did not get along very well because there was a lack of just understanding the circumstances.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was not altogether happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when they decided that things are getting bad again, that the Communists were gaining power and that the future was not bright for them-- he was an owner of a textile mill.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were giving him difficulty to return it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He decided to emigrate again with his family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when they did, I moved back to the Becks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "To their credit, I have to say that they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all conspired, so to speak, to ship me out also.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They felt that the future was not in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both, both families.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my aunt, who was a great entrepreneur, did a lot of running around to get papers for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the Becks finished the job to get permission that I leave the country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this effort was redoubled in February of 1948 when the Communists took over the government in the Putsch and ended the three years of democracy that the republic enjoyed.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
